---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="About - TechBlog"
  description="Learn more about TechBlog and our mission to share modern web development knowledge"
>
  <article class="about-content">
    <h1>About TechBlog</h1>

    <section class="intro">
      <p>
        Welcome to TechBlog, your premier destination for modern web development insights,
        tutorials, and best practices. We're passionate about sharing knowledge and helping
        developers build better, faster, and more accessible web applications.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="mission">
      <h2>Our Mission</h2>
      <p>
        Our mission is to demystify modern web development and make cutting-edge techniques
        accessible to developers of all skill levels. We believe that by sharing knowledge
        and fostering a community of learning, we can collectively push the boundaries of
        what's possible on the web.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="topics">
      <h2>What We Cover</h2>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Modern Frameworks:</strong> Deep dives into Astro, React, Vue, and other popular frameworks</li>
        <li><strong>Performance Optimization:</strong> Techniques for building lightning-fast websites</li>
        <li><strong>Static Site Generation:</strong> Leveraging SSG for better performance and SEO</li>
        <li><strong>Web Standards:</strong> Staying up-to-date with the latest web platform features</li>
        <li><strong>Best Practices:</strong> Component architecture, TypeScript, testing, and more</li>
        <li><strong>CSS & Design:</strong> Modern styling approaches and responsive design patterns</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section class="technology">
      <h2>Built with Astro</h2>
      <p>
        This blog is proudly built with <a href="https://astro.build" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Astro</a>,
        a modern static site generator that delivers exceptional performance by shipping zero JavaScript
        by default. Astro's component-based architecture and partial hydration make it perfect for
        content-heavy sites like blogs.
      </p>
      <div class="tech-features">
        <div class="feature">
          <h3>Fast by Default</h3>
          <p>Astro renders pages to static HTML at build time, resulting in blazing-fast load times.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="feature">
          <h3>Component Islands</h3>
          <p>Add interactivity only where needed with Astro's partial hydration architecture.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="feature">
          <h3>Framework Agnostic</h3>
          <p>Use React, Vue, Svelte, or any other framework alongside Astro components.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="contact">
      <h2>Get In Touch</h2>
      <p>
        Have questions, suggestions, or topics you'd like us to cover? We'd love to hear from you!
        Connect with us on social media or reach out through our contact channels.
      </p>
    </section>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .about-content {
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  h1 {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    text-align: center;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
    -webkit-background-clip: text;
    -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
    background-clip: text;
  }

  section {
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
  }

  h2 {
    font-size: 1.8rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    color: #667eea;
  }

  h3 {
    font-size: 1.3rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  p {
    line-height: 1.8;
    color: #444;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  ul {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
  }

  ul li {
    padding: 0.75rem 0;
    border-bottom: 1px solid #e0e0e0;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  ul li:last-child {
    border-bottom: none;
  }

  .intro {
    background: #f8f9fa;
    padding: 2rem;
    border-radius: 8px;
    border-left: 4px solid #667eea;
  }

  .tech-features {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(200px, 1fr));
    gap: 1.5rem;
    margin-top: 1.5rem;
  }

  .feature {
    background: white;
    padding: 1.5rem;
    border-radius: 8px;
    box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
  }

  .feature h3 {
    color: #667eea;
    margin-top: 0;
  }

  .feature p {
    margin: 0;
    font-size: 0.95rem;
  }

  a {
    color: #667eea;
    font-weight: 500;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    h1 {
      font-size: 2rem;
    }

    h2 {
      font-size: 1.5rem;
    }

    .tech-features {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
  }
</style>
